<paragraph id="9948EFABF33B75200216B904773EF6EF" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4BBFE85B96C89423639046FB264C61E5" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BOLIVIA. Tarija, 1904, 
<emphasis id="400020363C612A86DC223DA9BCCBABA8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">K. Fiebrig</emphasis>
2655A (holotype BM000758194, isotypes K, P).
